{"text": " Welcome to QM3 training by all here. It is designed to train in six rounds consisting of three minutes each with one minute break in between. The purpose of this particular training is to train the ability to quickly mobilize meditative attention towards the same meditative state. This practice is centered on witnessing the presence of air, a fine and invisible object. We will now begin in ten seconds. Let's observe the presence of air in front of you. Since the presence of air, the presence of air does not follow. Although it is movement, don't follow your breathing, just witness the presence of air in front of your face. Do not follow the air. Do not follow your breathing, witness the presence of air. The air is moving on its own. The body is breathing by itself. You are just the witness, how it is all happening by itself. Just witness the presence of air in front of you. Do not follow your breathing, witness the presence of air in front of you.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 2.000000000000001, "end": 7.02, "text": " Welcome to QM3 training by all here.", "tokens": [50364, 4027, 281, 1249, 44, 18, 3097, 538, 439, 510, 13, 50844], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.19155637841475637, "compression_ratio": 1.247787610619469, "no_speech_prob": 0.14261195063591003, "words": [{"word": " Welcome", "start": 2.000000000000001, "end": 3.2, "probability": 0.9215549826622009}, {"word": " to", "start": 3.2, "end": 3.5, "probability": 0.9972557425498962}, {"word": " QM3", "start": 3.5, "end": 4.38, "probability": 0.8934799631436666}, {"word": " training", "start": 4.38, "end": 5.22, "probability": 0.4965609014034271}, {"word": " by", "start": 5.22, "end": 5.96, "probability": 0.862299382686615}, {"word": " all", "start": 5.96, "end": 6.34, "probability": 0.7051928639411926}, {"word": " here.", "start": 6.34, "end": 7.02, "probability": 0.9685048460960388}]}, {"id": 1, "seek": 0, "start": 8.4, "end": 21.06, "text": " It is designed to train in six rou